headline: Cintas Corporation Opens Nominations for the 12th Annual Nationwide Custodian of the Year Contest
summary: CINCINNATI, January 13, 2025--Cintas launched its 12th annual Cintas Custodian of the Year contest, which honors exceptional school custodians.
